Paramedics found the man in a critical condition after his leg became trapped inside a machine. CAPE TOWN A man has sustained critical injuries in a freak work accident at work.Paramedics were called to assist the man at a business near Worcester on Thursday night.They found the man in a critical condition after his leg became trapped inside a machine.ER24 s Russel Meiring says: Paramedics and Metro Rescue workers found the man on the scene and treated him for a serious leg injury and provided him with advanced life support. (Edited by Leeto M Khoza)